This is a framework for making a node js website with express.

===
Installing node
==
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install python-software-properties python g++ make
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:chris-lea/node.js
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install nodejs

===
Updating npm (already installed with node.js)
===
* Check version
npm --version
* Update version
sudo npm install npm -g

===
Installing express
===
sudo npm install -g express
